            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I have had the privilege of working at Bubble Blue, I am pleased to share my positive experiences with this exceptional institution.\nBubble Blue truly embraces Montessori principles, creating an environment where individualised learning thrives. The classrooms are thoughtfully designed to encourage independence and foster a love for learning.\n\nThe school excels in cultivating a nurturing and respectful atmosphere, which enhances the overall educational experience and helps children to grow up as responsible people.\nThe commitment to staff development is evident through continuous opportunities for Montessori-specific training. This dedication ensures that the teachers remain well-equipped to provide proper care and support to the children.\n\nMy time at Bubble Blue was incredibly rewarding, and I am confident that the school’s ongoing commitment to Montessori education and its supportive staff will continue to provide an exceptional learning environment.\n\nThank you for allowing me to be part of this inspiring educational journey.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
